Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:10.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, little friends! You're singing this oh so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:15.28,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, it is a very beautiful day today, certainly, something worth singing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:19.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There's music in the treetops, \N And there's music in the vale,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:23.87,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And all around me music fills the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:28.15,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There's music by the river,\NAnd there's music in the grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:32.80,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And the music makes your heart soar in reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:59.33,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.59,0:01:01.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You are too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.74,0:01:11.55,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You… Um… You didn't hear me… Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:14.36,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Singing in the most beautiful voice ever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:15.83,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we did!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:04.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've never heard you sing a solo like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.73,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It was like a little slice of heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:09.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,With ice-cream on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy! I cannot believe your spectacular voice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.76,Rarity,,0,0,0,,isn't part of the Ponytones quartet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:17.57,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:22.77,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Especially since you hired us to perform for your Pet Center Fundraiser tomorrow night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:25.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This simply must be rectified!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You must share that stunning voice at the event!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It will be so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.76,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You will be there on stage! Basking in the hooflights!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:38.09,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The center of attention! A shining star!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:41.02,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,With everypony staring at you! Judging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Jealously noting how they can be way better than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.64,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Why wasn't it them?! Why wasn't it them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:51.65,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And then, when you choke, they'll turn on you becoming a seething, angry mob, and you'll be horribly humiliated!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:54.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Never able to show your face in Ponyville again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:55.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.80,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.03,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But I'm so good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:02.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Come, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:07.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You will join the group making the Pony Tones quartet the Pony Tones quintet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.33,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Pardon me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I love the Ponytones, I'm one of their biggest fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:17.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but I do not want to perform with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Why not, Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.84,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:24.22,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I… I have…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,um… I… I have…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.04,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.53,0:03:31.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I have stage fright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.08,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Is it contagious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Stage fright isn't a disease, Pinkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:40.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It just means that Fluttershy is scared to perform in front of everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.91,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm very thankful the Ponytones are singing at the Pet Center fundraiser
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:46.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,and I'm really looking forward to the performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.75,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,but I'll be watching safely from the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:54.70,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, I think it is a terrible waste of an exquisite talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:57.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but I understand that you're not comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:01.18,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, Angel's right. We'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of work to do before the tomorrow's event.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:21.05,Rarity,,0,0,0,,All right, Ponytones, let's run through that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:35.54,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Everypony's saying you should learn to express your voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:38.40,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,But if talk doesn't seems like it's the answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Luckily you have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:45.34,Somepony,,0,0,0,,When you find you've got the music, \N Got the music in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:49.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Find you've got the music,\NGot the music in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Rarity, you were awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:05:00.73,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Spike, but this is an ensemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nah, the rest of you were pretty good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:08.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought you were all amazing, Pony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.24,AppleRose,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:13.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now, Pony Tones, I want you all to rest your voices for the remainder of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:17.30,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We'll do a final run-through tomorrow before the big event. Alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.25,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.38,AppleRose,,0,0,0,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rarity, the Pony Tones are really gonna make
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.13,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,the Ponyville Pet Center fundraiser so special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:29.43,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for helping me help the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:30.38,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:35.18,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It is wonderful when a plan comes together without any sort of drama. Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.22,AppleRose,,0,0,0,,Morning, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:59.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Pony Tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:03.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Actually, we are the Pony Tones minus one tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:05.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Big Mac is inconveniently late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:15.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well there you are. Haven't I told you about punctuality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:33.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Big Mac, can you please start the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:35.45,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,N-nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.93,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Big Mac, did you lose your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.48,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,E-eyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.88,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What ever did you do to cause this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.88,0:06:50.04,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:53.01,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Howdy, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:57.07,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And welcome to the twelfth Annual Ponyville Turkey Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:03.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Who will take the title this year? Will it be somepony new?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:11.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Or will the turkey call champion of six years defend his title to make it lucky number seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:16.04,Granny Smith,,0,0,0,,We'll find out if you stop your gabbling and get on with the garbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.41,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Allright, everypony. Let's talk turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:21.77,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Big Mac, you're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.06,Rarity,,0,0,0,,A turkey call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You lost your voice doing a…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.84,Rarity,,0,0,0,,turkey call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Lost his voice and the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.64,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now we can't perform tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We what? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:46.41,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You have to perform! Otherwise the fundraiser will be a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't perform tonight with only three voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:50.32,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It will take rearranging all the music, and we just don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Fluttershy, but I have no remedy for this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:02.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Of course! A remedy! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:21.68,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I can cure this pony that is hoarse.\N But it will take a longer course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:23.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:29.82,Zecora,,0,0,0,,I can mix a brew that will work just right.\NBut it cannot heal him by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:35.42,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Where are we ever gonna find a deep voice to replace Big Mac's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.92,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Zecora, but this is no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:45.29,Rarity,,0,0,0,,We need a bass voice for the harmonies to work! \N Without it the performance will be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:51.22,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Please, forgive my strange elation,\NBut I was not laughing at your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:56.16,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Remember when you pony folk\NStumbled into poison joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:09:01.66,Zecora,,0,0,0,,Miss Fluttershy had an unusual change\NDeepening her vocal range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:04.02,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.52,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:10.17,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Your voice became really low, making it sound like…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.83,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,…Flutterguy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:17.13,Zecora,,0,0,0,,With these leaves I can mix a brew\NCreating the same effect on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Zecora, that's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:23.40,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll do it. I'll do anything for the animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:26.12,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, you'd even appear on stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.38,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh. Except that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.63,0:09:33.58,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I just can't bring myself to sing on stage in front of everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:38.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What if you sang not in front of everypony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:43.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What if Big Mac was on stage, moving his lips,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.23,Rarity,,0,0,0,,while you're behind the curtains, singing his part?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,It will be just like singing in your house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Nopony would know it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.43,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Even still, I just don't think I could sing in front of…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:56.24,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You must! For the animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.73,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Mix it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now, do it just like we practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:28.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Good evening, citizens of Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.61,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you all for coming out tonight and generously
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,supporting the Ponyville Pet Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:37.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Thanks to your kindness, pets are finding loving homes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,and we are sure to meet our fundraising goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:41.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where is Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:45.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Probably hiding, you know how much this pony hates the spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,So, with no further ado
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:52.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,please welcome "'The Pony Tones"!
