Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:34.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Then it happens suddenly, \NThe music takes you over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:38.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And you find you've got the music \N Got the music in you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:43.44,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Find you've got the music \N Got the music in you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.60,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Everypony saying you should \N Learn to express your voice
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:54.36,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But if talk does not seem like it's the answer\NLuckily you have a choice
