Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:04.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Find you've got the music \N Got the music in you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.53,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Got the music
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.64,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Got the music in you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:31.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Pony Tones, that was truly amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:34.22,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And you sounded better than ever, big brother
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:40.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, you were on the wrong side of the curtain, you totally missed the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:44.79,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Just like a true professional,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:48.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy was backstage, making sure everything ran smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And it was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:53.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That was fantastic, Pony Tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:57.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,My new puppy and I thought it was super duper crazy good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why thank you.
