Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:32.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh Rarity, we can't disappoint that sweet little filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you are up for it?
