Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:46.43,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Find you've got the music \NGot the music in you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Got the music
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Got the music in you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:56.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right, we got the Pony Tones, we got the Pony Tones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:03.07,Mayor,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Pony Tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.74,Mayor,,0,0,0,,And it would be even more amazing if you could perform
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:08.36,Mayor,,0,0,0,,at my ribbon-cutting ceremony tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:12.54,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mayor, we would love to, but…
