Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.90,Mayor,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:24.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Fluttershy, you don't have to perform again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:27.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But we wouldn't want to disappoint the mayor.
