Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.06,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We wouldn't want to disappoint the school ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:21.81,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Find the music deep down in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:26.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You can find it. Oh yeah. \NGot the music in you now.
