Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:48.76,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:57.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Now you can bathe in the poison joke antidote and sound like your lovely self again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.49,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.49,0:16:04.48,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that last performance was my last performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.16,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:13.72,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Would it be ok if Fluttershy sang for you one last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:18.45,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
