Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:25.73,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.52,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Flutterguy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.15,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:27.65,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.06,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.17,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And that shy filly was leaving her dream in the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:32.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,because she couldn't bring herself to coming to the spolight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:32.83,Big Mac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:36.43,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Well, for corn's sake, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.69,0:17:40.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:41.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:43.77,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:45.92,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,That was totally unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:50.46,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I mean! The curtain came up and there you were singing in front of everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:54.91,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And you know? I don't think anypony was jealous, cause there certainly wasn't an angry mob!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.31,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,But it must have been horrible to standing on a stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.97,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,All eyes glued directly on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.70,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,It's like you were living your own personal worst nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:06.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.19,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.28,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:18.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What Pinkie meant to say was that you were really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.06,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Wait! Didn't I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:21.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Hardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.25,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.38,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You totally blew my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.48,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:34.79,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Though, no offence, you kind of sounded like a dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:39.74,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,A great sounding dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:44.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:52.94,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Because I'm never going to sing in front of anypony ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.61,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.11,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Can we please stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.62,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I just don't understand why, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,After all, you are the one that wanted the Pony Tones
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:10.58,Rarity,,0,0,0,,to sing for every silly thing that was requested of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.96,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You mean you knew I really wanted to perform?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of course I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:21.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And for all her babbling, Pinkie Pie was right about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:22.47,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Only one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:26.55,Rarity,,0,0,0,,When that curtain fell and everypony saw you singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.56,Rarity,,0,0,0,,you lived your worst nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.37,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Was it really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:32.16,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:34.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, what was so bad about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.56,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,The thunderous applause?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.67,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,The praise for your fantastic singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:41.60,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,The screaming fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:54.29,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There is music in the tree tops \NAnd there's music in the vale
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:58.76,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And all around the music fills the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:03.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There's music by the river \NAnd there's music in the grass
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:07.30,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,And the music makes your heart soar in reply
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:10.64,Somepony,,0,0,0,,When you find you've got the music…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:13.35,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You've got to look inside and find
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:15.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,When you find you've got the music…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.92,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The music deep inside you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:20.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…you've got the music…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:22.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,One time you look inside you'll see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…you've got the music…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:27.66,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You're gonna find it, gonna find
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:32.08,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You've got the music, got the music, got the music in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:40.01,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You did it, Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,See? That wasn't so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:46.15,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And you didn't look completely petrified by the fact that we were all staring at you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:50.60,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:51.71,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:53.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Fantastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:56.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,because the Pony Tones have been booked
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,for the Apple family Zap Apple jam extraordinaire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.04,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh no,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.24,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.76,Somepony,,0,0,0,,How comes, Fluttershy? Really? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.50,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I'll get there someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:12.70,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But for now baby steps, everypony, baby steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:19.55,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Sometimes being afraid can stop you from doing something that you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:24.09,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But hiding behind these fears means you are only hiding from your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:31.38,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It's much better to face those fears so you can shine and be the best pony you can possibly be.
